GameMap(char[][], boolean, int, boolean) - Constructor for class dkeep.logic.GameMap
Constructor for a Game level Map array is the matrix for the game map MultipleOgres is a boolean that informs the constructor if it has to randomly generate the multiple ogres While nOgres is self explanatory being the number of ogres InstantaneousDoorOpen is a boolean that informs the constructor if it has to open door instantaneously, for example, with a lever
